Name: Febo
Review Text: An excellent sit-in / take out branch of this chain cafe selling all the usual Dutch products. Spotlessly clean, toilets available and staff are extremely friendly.  Well worth a stop here when visiting the Dapper Market

Name: Febo
Review Text: Totally worth the calories. I crave this every other day and have to refrain from indulging my  cravings. The sate croquette is my favorite. Easy, quick, convenient, and Dutch.

Review Text: You get what you pay for. Decent fast food, FEBO chicken is tastier than that of KFC's. Plenty of seats to eat in.
